  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK183">
<l>puṟaṅkūṟip poyttuyir vāḻtaliṟ cāta</l>
<l>laṟamkūṟu mākkan tarum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Death rather than life will confer upon the deceitful backbiter the profit which (the treatises on) virtue point out.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
